title: Jonny Craig - New songs 2013/Demo's 2012
description:
This is my collection of all the officially released songs and previously leaked 

demo's for Jonny Craig's solo project since the release of his debut album.


The torrent is split into 2 parts named "Demo's 2013" & "New 2013".


Songs in the demo's folder are the roughly recorded versions leaked end of 2012

Songs in the new folder are songs he has officially released/put on youtube 2013 


Track listing:


Demo's 2012


1. When it Rains it Pours

2. I Belong out Here

3. Just Another Whore

4. Rhythm to my Soul

5. Nobody Ever Will (Live) - Recorded by myself when he came over to the UK 2012


New 2013


1. Cry me a River (Justin Timberlake Cover)

2. House of War

3. Nobody Ever Will (Studio Version)

4. Rhythm in my Soul (Studio Version)

5. The Lives we Live



I often find some things dont ever get put on piratebay and i need to go looking 

through the vast internet space for them so thought id give back to the poor souls 

who find themselves in the same situation often.


Currently going through my music collection and uploading anything i can remember 

having to go elsewhere to find.


Requests Welcome.


Enjoy! :)
